sections.comments: BA MUSC majors and all MUSC minors must email the MUSC Advisor at music.advisor@ubc.ca to register. Students ineligible to register for this class without instructor permission, should register for the WAITING LIST MUSC 120 1W1. If you have difficulty registering, email the MUSC Advisor at music.advisor@ubc.ca. Must read music.2020W Format:  Every week, students study online course materials on their own time (asynchronously).Every week they must attend a 20-minute online tutorial, chosen freely from several sessions that will be held between 9:30 and 11 am on Tuesdays and Thursdays.

description: An overview of Western music from antiquity through the Middle Ages and Renaissance, providing a framework for understanding musical styles and practices, and examining selected compositions in greater analytical and historical depth.
